{"tid":2101971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲撤港引渡協議  留學生、臨時工簽證延至五年","createTime":"2020-07-10T06:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:59:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1e3ec22a27b46f23e19caa7d6bc3a83511dde2","tid":2101971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:59:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/437RNM2TNWFKUESIWQWKRIVOLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2F437RNM2TNWFKUESIWQWKRIVOLI%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=9eba30a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2F437RNM2TNWFKUESIWQWKRIVOLI%2F&h=ed220539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/437RNM2TNWFKUESIWQWKRIVOLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n澳洲撤港引渡協議 <br />\n留學生、臨時工簽證延至五年<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法剝奪香港人基本人權，再有外國出手協助。澳洲總理莫里森昨日宣佈暫停跟香港的引渡協議之餘，延長給予兩種港人簽證有效期限至五年，為取得澳洲永久居留權鋪路；新西蘭亦正檢視與香港的關係。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森表示，「港版國安法的實施，從根本改變了我們跟香港達成引渡協議的環境」，宣佈即日暫停與香港之間的引渡協議。他又表示更新了對香港的旅遊警示，呼籲國民不要到香港，形容港版國安法覆蓋面廣泛，法例詳情未明，澳洲人可能有被捕風險，甚至被引渡到中國大陸扣押。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YMLFCNdrXmZ5zurMAqUc7Ur0s5s=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZMQRBU5TOJ6THDL2FJ7KXH6ZEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYMLFCNdrXmZ5zurMAqUc7Ur0s5s%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZMQRBU5TOJ6THDL2FJ7KXH6ZEM.jpg&h=d93e34f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲總理莫里森<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SLp_pSsYmQT8hZwOAG_3eeZl2GY=/639x827/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/73XR7YNARQQ7CG6NN3TSMEH3SQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSLp_pSsYmQT8hZwOAG_3eeZl2GY%3D%2F639x827%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F73XR7YNARQQ7CG6NN3TSMEH3SQ.jpg&h=c8f0b510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國國家主席習近平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k7mgjOtcfqqwUT5bS1UioS1rAXI=/640x432/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GRURNRAM3YOE54UGSPDR5DOBYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk7mgjOtcfqqwUT5bS1UioS1rAXI%3D%2F640x432%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGRURNRAM3YOE54UGSPDR5DOBYU.jpg&h=5e286a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅強烈譴責澳洲改變對港簽證政策。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逗留五年可申永久居留權<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五眼聯盟外長討論港狀況<br />\n<br />\n他又指：「相信會有香港人想移居其他地方、在其他地方展開<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n在當地居住五年，再申請永久居留。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森表示，坎培拉政府「不預期短期內會有大批港人申請」。根據<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n優先。澳洲未有為香港人提供任何人道簽證。<br />\n<br />\n在新南威爾斯省讀大學的港人<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，卻因疫情未能返回澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n對於澳洲改變對港簽證政策，中國極度不滿。<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n否則必將「搬起石頭砸自己的腳」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oHgHjLH5a_vNno6x5p3OY4DWg6A=/595x595/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MVPPTGPLMOPCNARALGXDSIUG4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoHgHjLH5a_vNno6x5p3OY4DWg6A%3D%2F595x595%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MVPPTGPLMOPCNARALGXDSIUG4.gif&h=365055b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a0Q2sR2MYd8sVPvxt0Xwxx6ComE=/595x928/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FI4ZUCWIBLZIQEJR4JTQEPG4LQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa0Q2sR2MYd8sVPvxt0Xwxx6ComE%3D%2F595x928%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFI4ZUCWIBLZIQEJR4JTQEPG4LQ.gif&h=ed4a76da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭檢視與港安排<br />\n<br />\n除了澳洲，鄰國新西蘭昨日亦緊隨澳洲步伐，<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n：「我們正審視有關引渡安排，但現已有足夠的安全保障。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社"},{"pid":"a1cdbcd1953b65044ebf06e665f6765d46e10806","tid":2101971,"uid":180293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"趙立堅呢排都好望下 華春瑩死咗去邊"},{"pid":"6fa90b27ac745c0ac25d82c9ad0d7e2508f307fb","tid":2101971,"uid":180293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趙立堅呢排都好忙下 華春瑩死咗去邊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"333414225fb46a3bcea0b1cc8e19177baed6e694","tid":2101971,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQOB8Ps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQOB8Ps.jpg&h=219e1de3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}